fuzzing_params.Constraints: 1 <= target.length <= 400, target consists only of lowercase English letters.

problem_info.title: 3324. Find the Sequence of Strings Appeared on the Screen
test_examples: Example 1: Input: target = "abc" Output: ["a","aa","ab","aba","abb","abc"] Explanation: The sequence of key presses done by Alice are: Press key 1, and the string on the screen becomes "a". Press key 1, and the string on the screen becomes "aa". Press key 2, and the string on the screen becomes "ab". Press key 1, and the string on the screen becomes "aba". Press key 2, and the string on the screen becomes "abb". Press key 2, and the string on the screen becomes "abc".
